## 🛡️ DEFENSIVE RECOMMENDATIONS

### Based on your successful attack, what would you recommend?

#### Physical Security:

- [ ] Implement mantrap entrances
- [ ] Require badge + PIN for all entries
- [ ] Security awareness training (anti-tailgating)
- [ ] Visitor escort policy
- [ ] Lock network closets
- [ ] Camera monitoring with active response

#### Network Security:

- [ ] Implement 802.1X (certificate-based network access)
- [ ] Segment networks (office ≠ servers ≠ ATMs)
- [ ] Disable unused ethernet ports
- [ ] Deploy Network Access Control (NAC)
- [ ] Monitor for unusual scanning activity
- [ ] Require VPN for database access

#### Detection & Response:

- [ ] Deploy SIEM for log correlation
- [ ] Set up IDS/IPS alerts
- [ ] Monitor for unauthorized devices
- [ ] Create incident response plan
- [ ] Regular penetration testing

